[30;1m85 | [0m[35m    Using StackView in an application is typically a simple matter of adding[0m

[30;1m86 | [0m[35m    the StackView as a child of a Window. The stack is usually anchored to the[0m
[30;1m87 | [0m[35m    edges of the window, except at the top or bottom where it might be anchored[0m
[30;1m88 | [0m[35m    to a status bar, or some other similar UI component. The stack can then be[0m
